    <title>ansible基础之inventory</title>
    <link href="https://njustlcx.github.io/2019/01/18/ansible%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B9%8Binventory/"/>
    <id>https://njustlcx.github.io/2019/01/18/ansible基础之inventory/</id>
